28/05/2003
ZAGREB, Croatia -- President Stipe Mesic praised the military Wednesday (28 May), marking Army Day and the Day of Land Forces. He noted the military's role in the country's struggle for independence and commended army participation in UN missions and in NATO's Partnership for Peace programme. (Vjesnik, Vecernji List - 28/05/03; HINA - 27/05/03)
